    <!-- Center -->
    <div class="center">
      <p>Since 2004, <%= @website %> has led the way in cashback and loyalty program marketing in Australia and New Zealand, providing fun and rewarding experiences for consumers while helping drive growth for our clients.</p>
      <p>In this time, we have run campaigns for some of the world’s most visible brands, helping them to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Boost profits</li>
        <li>Gain market share</li>
        <li>Raise product awareness and brand visibility</li>
        <li>Increase sales</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

