      <p>By providing end-to-end solutions, we can also offer a cost-effective way to expand your marketing activity. Using our years of experience and detailed sector knowledge, we have all the tools required to make sure delivery is as smooth as possible.</p>
      <p><%= @website %> is a division of Pro-Logic International, a promotional management company operating across Australia and New Zealand.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
